  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_step.text_1": "Press [Dodge] to consume stamina and perform a [Step].\nShort distance, swift response, and minimal recovery time. Grants i-frames.",

  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_roll.header": "Dodge: Roll",
  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_roll.text_1": "Press [Dodge] to consume stamina and perform a [Roll].\nCovers a longer distance but leaves a larger opening upon recovery. Grants i-frames.",

  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_technician.header": "Passive: Technician",
  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_technician.text_1": "Evading an incoming attack at the absolute last split-second...",
  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_technician.text_2": "...will trigger a [Perfect Dodge], instantly refunding the stamina consumed!",

  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_guard.header": "Guard",
  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_guard.text_1": "Hold [Guard] to enter a defensive stance\nconsuming [Stamina] to block frontal melee attacks.\n \nConsecutive blocks will rapidly drain your [Stamina]",

  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_guard_break.header": "Guard Break",
  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_guard_break.text_1": "Relying purely on your guard\nis rarely a wise choice...",
  "epic_fight_ponder.ponder.skill_guard_break.text_2": "Taking heavy blows when depleting your [Stamina]\nwill result in a devastating [Guard Break] stagger.",

